From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sebastien DUMETZ <s.dumetz@holusion.com>
Date: Tue, 17 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 7/7] fix xwayland associate listener leak on destroy

Remove associate and dissociate listeners in
handle_xwayland_surface_destroy to prevent assertion failure in
wlroots xwm.c when closing xwayland windows.
---
 xwayland.c | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/xwayland.c b/xwayland.c
index 53eac1e..0000000 100644
--- a/xwayland.c
+++ b/xwayland.c
@@ -139,6 +139,8 @@ handle_xwayland_surface_destroy(struct wl_listener *listener, void *data)
 	struct cg_view *view = &xwayland_view->view;
 
 	wl_list_remove(&xwayland_view->destroy.link);
+	wl_list_remove(&xwayland_view->associate.link);
+	wl_list_remove(&xwayland_view->dissociate.link);
 	wl_list_remove(&xwayland_view->request_fullscreen.link);
 	xwayland_view->xwayland_surface = NULL;
 
